changelog.change_log:
This update focuses on enhancing gameplay based on recent playtests and user feedback. 
Were added comprehensive explanations of game mechanics and resolved numerous bugs.

Updates list :

New features:
- New tutorial stage with damage multiplier mechanic description;
- New panel with list of all challenges and completion status;
- Click on (B) button during a challenge to show current mission progress;
- Added texts with game hints and advice in a transition screen;
- Level of game difficulty now is available in the Settings menu;

Fixes and Changes:
- UX improvements in the "Demons Fort" story level;
- Bugfixes and more description in Tutorial stages;
- Added story challenges to completed list 
for correct calculation of the total completed challenges count;
- Moved arcade modes under a separate menu panel "Custom Mode";
- Improved UI/UX in the challenge selection panel;
- Fixed an epic weapon quality raycast-based scope behavior;
- Corrected a head IK animations after an enemy takes damage;
- Changed announcer voice and SFX for story levels
